Develop environment setup in Linux:

install ccnx, ccnx-cpp from github.com/named-data/
for ccnx:
	sudo apt-get install libssl-dev
	sudo apt-get install libexpat1-dev
	sudo apt-get install libpcap-dev
for ccnx-cpp:
	sudo apt-get install libboost1.53-all-dev

install mongodb:
	following official instructions
install mongodb c++ driver:
	download official c++ driver source files
	install: in mongo-cxx-driver-vx.x: sudo scons install
